    <div class="background-img1"></div>
    <section class="feature-wrapper">
        <img class="singularity-title-img" src="Images/FeaturedProjects/Singularity_Logo.png" />
        <div class="content1 black-background">
            <h2 class="textpadding">"The card game of total control. Every decision - and accompanying consequence - is your own."</h2>

            <p class="body-text textpadding">
                Stop waiting for the perfect draw and join me for a new type of card game with <strong>no randomness.</strong>
                </p>
            <p class="body-text textpadding">
                play your deck in the order you decide, and pull off your favorite combos every single game.
                Dive into intense 1v1 duels, strategic team battles, chaotic free-for-alls, or thrilling cooperative and solo boss incursions.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

