            <strong>Game Designer:</strong> Playtested, created, and iterated on expansions and co-op content. Assisted in polishing the core set.
        </p>
        <ul class="textpadding">
            <li>
                <p class="body-text"> refined designs through simplification and goal-oriented evaluation</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p class="body-text">
                    sketched wireframes inspired by successful implementations in other Tabletop Simulator games
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p class="body-text">
                    Iteratively refined automation mechanics, adapting the experience to match the expectations and habits of Tabletop Simulator users
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p class="body-text">
                    Garnered enthusiastic support from over 1,000 backers on Gamefound.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p class="body-text">
                    Successfully held the first official Singularity tournament via Tabletop Simulator.
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="white-background">
        <div class="links textpadding">
